Encouraged to so many people with epilepsy, to open out, to talk about their epilepsy, and to come out of the stigma with the help of support group. 2. Helped to led a normal life, even if someone from the family is suffering with epilepsy. 3. Have arranged 28 marriages of all the people with epilepsy history. 4. Are helping 100 needy people with epilepsy for their medications. 5. Helped to create awareness in the society.
